@startuml system-context-overview

title 系統上下文概覽圖

actor "客戶" as Customer
actor "賣家" as Seller
actor "管理員" as Admin
actor "配送員" as DeliveryPerson

package "GenAI Demo 電商系統" as System {
    component "客戶管理服務" as CustomerService
    component "產品管理服務" as ProductService
    component "訂單管理服務" as OrderService
    component "支付服務" as PaymentService
    component "配送服務" as DeliveryService
    component "通知服務" as NotificationService
}

package "外部系統" as ExternalSystems {
    component "支付閘道" as PaymentGateway
    component "物流系統" as LogisticsSystem
    component "簡訊服務" as SMSService
    component "電子郵件服務" as EmailService
    component "第三方認證" as AuthService
}

' 使用者與系統的互動
Customer --> CustomerService : 註冊/登入
Customer --> ProductService : 瀏覽商品
Customer --> OrderService : 下訂單
Customer --> PaymentService : 付款

Seller --> ProductService : 管理商品
Seller --> OrderService : 處理訂單
Seller --> DeliveryService : 安排配送

Admin --> System : 系統管理
DeliveryPerson --> DeliveryService : 更新配送狀態

' 系統與外部服務的整合
PaymentService --> PaymentGateway : 處理付款
DeliveryService --> LogisticsSystem : 物流追蹤
NotificationService --> SMSService : 發送簡訊
NotificationService --> EmailService : 發送郵件
CustomerService --> AuthService : 第三方登入

note right of System
  核心電商功能
  - 使用者管理
  - 商品管理
  - 訂單處理
  - 支付處理
  - 配送管理
  - 通知服務
end note

note right of ExternalSystems
  外部整合服務
  - 金流服務
  - 物流服務
  - 通訊服務
  - 認證服務
end note

@enduml